    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 <strong>Sokocat - Islands</strong> 是一款迷人的益智冒险游戏，你将引导一只可爱的猫咪穿越宁静的小岛，挑战巧妙设计的谜题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精准推动方块，解决简约却充满逻辑的难题。每一步都至关重要——仔细思考，探索路径，找出最佳解法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/f3e02b9072c95c8ff2bba519bedf837e.poster.avif?t=1754088576\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/f3e02b9072c95c8ff2bba519bedf837e.webm?t=1754088576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/f3e02b9072c95c8ff2bba519bedf837e.mp4?t=1754088576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配合治愈的画面风格和轻松的音乐，<i>Sokocat - Islands</i> 非常适合喜爱逻辑思维、平静氛围与萌系角色的玩家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/8694ba6f447f923961d0a55bdc9b6854.poster.avif?t=1754088576\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/8694ba6f447f923961d0a55bdc9b6854.webm?t=1754088576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/8694ba6f447f923961d0a55bdc9b6854.mp4?t=1754088576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✨ 游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 简单直观的操作方式<br>• 50 个精心设计的关卡，从简单到具有挑战性<br>• 可解锁成就系统<br>• 可爱猫咪担任主角！</p>",
